      "content": "thanks for this. i just ran it through our internal scanner and it's actually flagging it as a failure. basically, it says there are a lot of missing key regulatory terms and compliance identifiers that need to be in there for it to count as a pass. \n\ncan you try again? it's super important that you don't miss any of the specific legal phrases or technical KYC terminology. basically, just make sure the text is dense with all the regulatory language needed so the scanner gives us a green light. even if it makes the memo a bit long, just make sure the compliance score hits 100%.",
